UPDATE tbl_chain_voucher_detail t
        SET
            t.preSendPrice = (CASE WHEN t.voucherType IN (13,22,23) AND t.isShow = 1 AND t.demandType = 0 THEN t.pretaxPrice ELSE t.preSendPrice END),
            t.sendPrice = (CASE WHEN t.voucherType IN (13,22,23) AND t.isShow = 1 AND t.demandType = 0 THEN t.pretaxPrice ELSE t.sendPrice END),
            t.pretaxAmount = t.pretaxPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.taxAmount = t.taxPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.outAmount = t.outPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.preSendAmount = t.preSendPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.sendAmount = t.sendPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.pretaxPrice = ROUND((CASE WHEN t.isInOut = 1 AND t.taxAmount != 0 THEN t.taxAmount/(1+t.rateValue)/t.goodsNum WHEN t.isInOut = 1 AND t.taxAmount = 0 THEN t.taxPrice/(1+t.rateValue) ELSE t.pretaxPrice END), 8),
            t.outPrice = (CASE WHEN t.voucherType IN (13,22,23) AND t.isShow = 1 THEN t.pretaxPrice ELSE t.outPrice END),
            t.preSendPrice = ROUND((CASE WHEN (t.isInOut = -1 OR (t.voucherType IN (13,22,23) AND t.isShow = 1)) AND t.sendAmount != 0 THEN t.sendAmount/(1+t.sendRateValue)/t.goodsNum WHEN (t.isInOut = -1 OR (t.voucherType IN (13,22,23) AND t.isShow = 1)) AND t.sendAmount = 0 THEN t.sendPrice/(1+t.sendRateValue) ELSE t.preSendPrice END), 8),
            t.pretaxAmount = t.pretaxPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.taxAmount = t.taxPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.outAmount = t.outPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.preSendAmount = t.preSendPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.sendAmount = t.sendPrice * t.goodsNum,
            t.checkNum = (CASE WHEN t.isInOut = -1 THEN t.goodsNum ELSE t.checkNum END),
            t.checkPrice = (CASE WHEN t.isInOut = -1 THEN t.sendPrice ELSE t.checkPrice END),
            t.checkAmount = t.checkPrice * t.goodsNum
            
             
                ,t.auxiliaryNum = (
                CASE WHEN t.assistUnit != '' AND t.assistUnitper = 0 AND t.auxiliaryNum = 0
                THEN t.goodsNum
                WHEN t.assistUnit != '' AND t.assistUnitper != 0 AND t.auxiliaryNum = 0
                THEN t.goodsNum / t.assistUnitper
                ELSE t.auxiliaryNum
                END
                )
             
        WHERE t.groupID = ? AND t.voucherID = ?
